{"word":"H3689 - כֶּסֶל - keçel - keh'-sel - Confidence","slug":"H3689","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כֶּסֶל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>keçel"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keh'-sel"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Confidence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05E1;&#x05DC; - kesel</b> - <i>keh'-sel</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3688\">H3688</a>; properly <i>fatness</i>, that is, by implication (literally) the <i>loin</i> (as the seat of the leaf <i>fat</i>) or (generally) the <i>viscera</i>; also (figuratively) <i>silliness</i> or (in a good sense) <i>trust: - </i>confidence, flank, folly, hope, loin."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3684\">H3684</a>, <a href=\"#/H3685\">H3685</a>, <a href=\"#/H3686\">H3686</a>, <a href=\"#/H3687\">H3687</a>, <a href=\"#/H3688\">H3688</a>, <a href=\"#/H3690\">H3690</a>, <a href=\"#/H3691\">H3691</a>, <a href=\"#/H3692\">H3692</a>, <a href=\"#/H3693\">H3693</a>, <a href=\"#/H3694\">H3694</a>, <a href=\"#/H3695\">H3695</a>, <a href=\"#/H3696\">H3696</a>"}]}